column1:
based on the api summary provided, it appears to be a currency conversion api. classified under the currency category:

```json
{
  "currency": [
    {
      "title": "converto-matic!",
      "description": "converto-matic! allows you to get exchange-rates for many currencies. it also makes it easy for you to know the value of your money in different currencies.",
      "endpoints": [
        {
          "type": "get",
          "endpoint": "/exchange",
          "description": "get exchange-rates from currency"
        },
        {
          "type": "get",
          "endpoint": "/convert",
          "description": "convert value from currency"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
